<p> <em>NME</em>在其续作的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/marvels-spider-man-2-review-3513197">五星级评论</a>中将<em>《漫威蜘蛛侠 2》</em>描述为“超级英雄游戏的新标准”，称赞其能够同时平衡“令人血脉喷张的动作”与“对悲伤和康复的强烈思考” 。</p><p> <em>Marvel 蜘蛛侠 2</em>将于 10 月 20 日在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PS5</a>上发布。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，Obsidian Entertainment 的工作室设计总监表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/pillars-of-eternity-director-wants-a-baldurs-gate-3-budget-for-the-third-game-3517936">只要预算符合<em>《博德之门 3</em> 》的预算，他就会制作《<em>永恒之柱 3》</em></a> 。</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/marvels-spider-man-2-is-getting-new-game-plus-in-a-post-launch-patch-3518001">&#39;Marvel&#39;s Spider-Man 2&#39; is getting new game plus in a post-launch patch</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
